narratives.question_text: What were your expectations for this studio and how well were they met?
comments: Considering the program for the final project, I expected this studio to be fun and unique, which it was. I was able to explore new methods of representation, which I will now carry on with me for projects in the future.

Given the brief, I expected the studio to be fun but also a challenge and perhaps push students out of their comfort zone as designers. I think that this a met and everyone produced exceptional work. The trip to Tokyo was also an amazing experience.
yes all, the trip was amazing, only it should have been longer a full 7 nights
